summary: This is a new, multi-level Dwemer dungeon with approximately 1 hour of playtime.  Filled with danger, traps, and the \"adventure of a lifetime!\"  (lol)
descriptionHtml: Follow the road west of Falkreath and you\'ll find Norzelfd, a colossal Dwemer site carved into the mountains. You\'ll plunder the depths, taking out the local competition of bandit scum before discovering the ruin\'s ancient, warfaring purpose - and the source of its power.
author: Stupiful
